  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't-- I don't feel Jewish anymore, nor do I want to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wanted to assimilate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wanted to be part of today's world without being pointed out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I've, I've, I've questioned that so many times, but luckily with the Hidden Children Conference where other hidden children are now coming out and, and, and, and telling about their feelings and I hear that they feel the same way about it, whether it's out of fear of being discovered again or whether it's just a backlash from what happened, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I am certainly not religious any longer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Tell us more about when you came to America.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we'll come back to the hidden children meetings that you have found.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, actually, at first, I, I-- America was never something that I was aspiring to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, I joined a Jewish organization, finally after the war called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're, they're a Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at that age, I was still able to, to-- I mean, to-- for my character and my beliefs, to be formed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In, in-- well, they-- they were quite big in Palestine at that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't Israel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was 1947.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in Belgium, in Brussels, they had a branch of [NON-ENGLISH] in Brussels.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in fact, many of the Jewish organization became quite known after the war, because they were also helping older Jews that they could find, all the survivors, putting it all together, giving them a sense of belonging.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And and that time, they were in a fight for their-- the Zionists, at least, were in a fight for their homeland.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
